name: Sarah Johnson
message: I'm very interested in the Modern Downtown Apartment. Could we schedule a viewing this week? I'm looking for a 2-bedroom place and this looks perfect. Also, are pets allowed?

name: Michael Chen
message: Hello! I'm interested in the Luxury Waterfront Condo. Is it still available? I'd like to know more about the amenities and if there are any additional fees for the pool and spa access.

name: Emily Rodriguez
message: The Victorian House caught my attention. I love the historic charm! When would be a good time to see it? Also, is the garden maintained by the landlord or tenant?

name: David Thompson
message: Hi, I'm relocating to New York for work and need an apartment by March 1st. The Modern Downtown Apartment looks ideal. Is it available for immediate occupancy?

name: Jessica Liu
message: I'm interested in the Contemporary Townhouse. The rooftop deck sounds amazing! Could you tell me more about the neighborhood and nearby schools?

name: Robert Wilson
message: My family and I are looking for a spacious home in Chicago. The Spacious Family Home seems perfect. Are the schools in the area highly rated? We have two young children.
